1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:01:56,660 --> 00:02:02,860
And The Winner Is Love

3
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:05,820
Episode 44

4
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,080
You’re right.

5
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:10,320
Did the killer

6
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,600
take these chiefs?

7
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,260
If that's the case,

8
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,600
Xue Lie

9
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,200
isn't just making an example of others.

10
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,760
There's something bigger going on

11
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,440
behind his moves.

12
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,400
Xia Qingmei!

13
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,400
Free me!

14
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,280
You!

15
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,120
Release me!

16
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,090
You rooted out my Sand Sect.

17
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,840
I won’t let you get away!

18
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,400
Isn’t that Leader Chong?

19
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,800
Shangguan Tou.

20
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,170
Lower your bows.

21
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,400
Leader!

22
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,400
It’s us.

23
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,960
Zhusha, Chequ?

24
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,580
Master Shangguan,

25
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,160
you…

26
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,520
you’re not…

27
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,000
It’s a long story.

28
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,330
What are you doing here?

29
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,800
We’re not alone.

30
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,520
They are all here.

31
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,160
We’re all here.

32
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,040
Leader Chong!

33
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,400
I never thought

34
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,730
I would meet you at here.

35
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,320
Haven’t I dismissed the disciples

36
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,450
after Hall of Flames were closed down?

37
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,840
What brings you here?

38
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,960
We know

39
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,930
that you did it for our sake.

40
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,320
You wanted us to stay away from the trouble

41
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,720
and live a peaceful life.

42
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,480
But Chequ and I

43
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,840
couldn’t just leave Hall of Flames.

44
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,280
So we planned

45
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,800
to settle down in Peace County

46
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,200
and then figure out a way.

47
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,520
Later, Xia Qingmei came to us,

48
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,280
saying that Sword Manor

49
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,400
would like to take us from Hall of Flames in.

50
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,040
So we gathered every one

51
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,120
we could find.

52
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,800
At present, some are hiding in Sword Manor,

53
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,680
the rest

54
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:04,080
come with us to find the missing disciples.

55
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,400
I don’t know

56
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,980
so many things have happened since then.

57
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,080
Leader Chong,

58
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,720
why are you

59
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,250
and Master Shangguan here?

60
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,320
And,

61
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,200
there are rumors

62
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,600
that Chief Guardian

63
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,800
has turned to Lord Lu?

64
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,720
Is it true?

65
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,920
Yuwen Muyuan

66
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,320
did turn to Xue Lie.

67
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,840
But,

68
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,720
last time when he came to Chequ and me,

69
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,440
-he…
-Wait.

70
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,640
You

71
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:35,960
met him?

72
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,400
When did you meet him?

73
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:38,880
It was

74
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:41,170
two days before Lin Fengzi’s wedding.

75
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,540
According to the date,

76
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,400
he has

77
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,060
turned to Lord Lu at that time.

78
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,200
But,

79
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,960
he told Chequ and me

80
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,960
that he would revive Hall of Flames.

81
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,360
He told you that?

82
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,560
Yes.

83
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,680
He

84
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:55,760
sent me away

85
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,920
and told Chequ in private.

86
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,640
Didn’t he?

87
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,050
He did say he’ll revive Hall of Flames.

88
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,360
Did he tell you anything else?

89
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,680
Did he tell you

90
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,210
how to revive Hall of Flames

91
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,000
or did he have a plan?

92
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,400
He never mentioned of a plan.

93
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,130
Nothing in particular?

94
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,640
Nothing.

95
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,680
I can’t believe

96
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:22,600
even the Chief Guardian betrayed Hall of Flames.

97
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,460
And he wounded Master Shangguan…

98
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,680
Gladly, you’re still alive.

99
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,210
I can’t expose my identity.

100
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,360
So please

101
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,620
keep it a secret for me.

102
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,720
Trust us.

103
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,600
By the way,

104
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,040
didn’t you settle down in Peace County?

105
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,880
What brings you to Mount Tianmushan?

106
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,680
Actually,

107
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,480
before Chief Guardian came to us,

108
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,680
we had planned to go back to Sword Manor.

109
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:48,010
He said he would revive Hall of Flames.

110
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,200
So we thought

111
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,130
we should gather all the disciples

112
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,560
and try

113
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,440
to find Nine Moves.

114
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,760
Have you found it?

115
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,360
Not yet.

116
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,360
We’ve been to so many places,

117
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,720
but found nothing.

118
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,320
Until recently,

119
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,400
several sects

120
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,280
were slaughtered by Nine Moves,

121
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,760
we predicted

122
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,880
that the murderer

123
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,880
must be the man who stole Nine Moves.

124
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,880
How did you find out

125
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,440
his next target

126
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,770
is the Purple Hawk Sect?

127
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,720
There’s a letter.

128
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,400
Do you know who sent it?

129
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,380
We don’t know if he’s a friend or a foe.

130
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,640
At least we know he and we

131
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,000
both want to stop the slaughter.

132
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,600
When we arrived at
Purple Hawk Sect headquarters,

133
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,960
they were all killed.

134
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,560
And then,

135
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,600
we met you.

136
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,680
Did you see the murderer’s face?

137
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,880
I saw that man’s back.

138
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:05,920
His back?

139
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,960
I didn’t see his face,

140
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:10,320
but he boasts his lightness of foot.

141
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,440
He jumped so swiftly

142
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,640
across the wall seizing Liang Henshui.

143
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,360
He must be much better than I am
in martial arts.

144
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,920
Of course he is.

145
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,160
You don’t say.

146
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,930
He’s grasped the ninth move of Nine Moves.

147
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,640
He’s not just better than you.

148
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,320
You’re a world of difference from him.

149
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,450
You misunderstand.

150
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,940
Nine Moves belongs to Hall of Flames.

151
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,000
But judging from his deft foot,

152
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,240
he isn’t one of us.

153
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,250
Instead, he’s like…

154
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,600
Like what?

155
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,560
Someone from Sword Manor.

156
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,640
Sword Manor?

157
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,340
How could anyone from Sword Manor

158
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,159
practice Nine Moves?

159
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:46,159
Has Uncle Lin turned to Xue Lie?

160
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:49,120
If Lin Zongxing has turned to Xue Lie,

161
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,240
that explains

162
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,250
why he picked Xue Lie’s side

163
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,120
on the wedding day

164
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,520
when Xue Lie announced the Sects Alliance.

165
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,940
But I don’t think it’s him.

166
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,160
When Xue Lie sent Imperial Guards to kill me,

167
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,680
Lin Zongxing tipped me to hold him hostage

168
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,330
so that I could get away.

169
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,000
If he turned to Xue Lie,

170
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,650
why would he help me?

171
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,560
I don’t believe it’s Uncle Lin, either.

172
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,490
As my uncle said,

173
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,440
Uncle Lin is a decent man.

174
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,480
Chequ,

175
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,400
I know you didn’t see his face.

176
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,280
What about his figure?

177
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,810
Do you think it’s Uncle Lin?

178
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,000
No, no, no.

179
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,520
He’s strong.

180
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,970
And he’s probably about my age.

181
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,960
He’s at your age

182
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,059
and boasts lightness of foot.

183
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,169
Only one meets the criteria

184
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,000
in Sword Manor.

185
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,760
Xia Qingmei.

186
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:40,409
Your Highness,

187
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:43,490
Liang Henshui has been locked in the dungeon.

188
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,840
Good job, Master Xia.

189
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,460
You’re my right-hand man.

190
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,800
In two days,

191
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,880
take him and He Qiliang

192
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,260
to the hunting field in the mountain.

193
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,160
The two of them

194
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,260
will complete the mission for me.

195
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,040
Yes.

196
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,480
Sugar-coated haws!

197
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,360
Tou, are you alright?

198
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,360
I’m fine.

199
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:16,280
After so many things happened lately,

200
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,120
there’s no time to grieve.

201
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,960
Take a look.

202
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,120
What is Fengzi doing here?

203
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,440
Sugar-coated haws!

204
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,920
Tou,

205
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,960
I’ll go meet her.

206
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,200
Go ahead.

207
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,490
She wouldn’t want to see me.

208
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,440
The jade is plain.

209
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,360
And there’s a crack on it.

210
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,960
I’ll give you two taels for it.

211
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,040
Sir,

212
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,320
would you please check it again?

213
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,600
My father gave it to me.

214
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,560
It’s made of prime jade.

215
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,200
How could you

216
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,400
give me only two taels?

217
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,840
Miss,

218
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,480
if you don’t like my offer,

219
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,080
please

220
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,400
inquire elsewhere.

221
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,480
All right.

222
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:20,400
Two taels it is.

223
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,520
We don’t want to pawn it anymore.

224
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,320
Xuezhi?

225
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,160
Fengzi,

226
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,000
I’ve learned

227
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,120
about the Tianling Stone from Tou.

228
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,450
Thank you for saving me.

229
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,480
The Tianling Stone

230
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,000
is of no use to me.

231
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,000
On the contrary,

232
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,940
it means responsibility.

233
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,440
It’s well applied

234
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,160
to save your life.

235
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,960
I’m so glad

236
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,420
to see you’re fine.

237
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:51,880
By the way, Xuezhi,

238
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,880
I’ve heard about

239
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,770
Master Shangguan’s death.

240
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,920
Don’t worry about me.

241
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,200
I’ve come through.

242
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,000
I should do something

243
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,440
to avenge Tou

244
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,560
other than

245
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,960
drown myself in pain.

246
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,240
Don’t do anything stupid.

247
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,680
The deceased can’t come back to life.

248
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,280
But you’ve got a life to live.

249
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,520
I’ll be fine.

250
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:18,810
I hope you will, too.

251
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:20,560
Fengzi,

252
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:22,160
are you married

253
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,020
to Xia Qingmei?

254
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,480
Great.

255
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,520
You’ve

256
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,600
always been the person he likes.

257
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,200
By the way,

258
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,320
why are you alone here?

259
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,040
Where is Xia Qingmei?

260
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:39,960
And

261
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,040
why did you go to the pawnshop?

262
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:44,170
Is everything alright in Sword Manor?

263
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,600
In fact,

264
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,040
Qingmei and I

265
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,080
have left Sword Manor.

266
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,800
Where do you live now?

267
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,040
In the suburb along the road

268
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,040
not far from here.

269
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,160
I see.

270
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,880
I have nothing to do now.

271
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,320
Why don’t I walk you back?

272
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:12,840
Fengzi,

273
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,360
you and Xia Qingmei

274
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,000
are living here?

275
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,240
Yes.

276
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,640
It’s not as comfortable as Sword Manor,

277
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,000
but I’m satisfied.

278
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,560
Have some tea.

279
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,720
Thanks.

280
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,760
Hey, Fengzi,

281
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,640
where is Xia Qingmei?

282
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,000
I don’t see him anywhere.

283
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,180
He hasn’t come back for weeks.

284
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,360
Well,

285
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,440
do you know where he is?

286
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,760
I don’t.

287
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,000
Maybe

288
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,620
he’s no command over himself.

289
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,800
What do you mean?

290
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,600
Did anything wrong

291
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,420
happen to Xia Qingmei?

292
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,760
Xuezhi,

293
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,560
actually,

294
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,360
I want to tell you something.

295
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,680
Hello, brother,

296
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:13,480
an uncle asks me to give it to you.

297
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:14,800
An uncle?

298
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:18,860
[Shangqing Sect is in danger]

299
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:21,360
Fengzi,

300
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:22,800
I know

301
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,960
Xia Qingmei is practicing

302
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,960
Nine Moves.

303
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,480
You know?

304
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,320
Is that why

305
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,480
you and Xia Qingmei

306
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,240
left Sword Manor?

307
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,800
My father was furious about it.

308
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,520
They had a terrible argument

309
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:40,260
Qingmei swore he’d never go back to Sword Manor.

310
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,010
I had no choice but to move out with him.

311
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,560
Do you know whom he learned

312
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:47,840
the Nine Moves from?

313
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,160
I don’t know

314
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,400
the details.

315
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,440
But I overheard them mention it.

316
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,400
I think Qingmei

317
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,320
saved

318
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:58,320
the monk who stole Nine Moves.

319
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:00,840
He learned it from the monk.

320
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:03,360
So it’s true Hong Sheng didn’t die that year.

321
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,560
Where is he now?

322
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,640
He was killed by Qingmei.

323
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,480
Xuezhi,

324
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:15,410
this is also why I told you about it.

325
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,720
Qingmei is behaving

326
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,700
more and more erratically

327
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,060
I’m worried about him.

328
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:23,480
I didn’t think much at the beginning.

329
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,320
I thought he was unhappy

330
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,760
and grumpy

331
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,200
because he felt unfulfilled

332
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,880
and made no progress in practice

333
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:31,940
after we moved out.

334
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:34,280
But in recent days,

335
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,460
his temper has been getting worse and worse.

336
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,520
He often smashes things

337
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:41,320
and complains about headaches.

338
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:43,840
One day,

339
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,080
I was so worried

340
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,040
so I followed him

341
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,280
and I saw…

342
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,320
Xia Qingmei

343
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,320
practicing Nine Moves

344
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:17,760
without the help of the Lotus Sutra.

345
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:18,880
I’m afraid

346
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,460
he’s fallen in deviation.

347
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,200
Xuezhi,

348
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:26,600
before he does anything unforgivable,

349
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:28,920
Would you please teach him Lotus Sutra?

350
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,120
Fengzi,

351
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,920
I would like to teach him,

352
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,640
but I’m afraid he has

353
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,840
Made a huge mistake.

354
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:42,880
What do you mean?

355
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,080
In the last month,

356
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:46,600
four sects

357
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,160
in the martial arts world

358
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:49,490
have been slaughtered.

359
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,880
And they all died of the ninth move

360
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,120
of Nine Moves.

361
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,840
I’m afraid

362
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,440
Xia Qingmei killed them all.

363
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:00,400
how can it be

364
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:04,360
Qingmei would never do that.

365
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,000
Qingmei is…

366
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,760
Xuezhi,

367
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:13,840
did you

368
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,920
come to Xiangzhou

369
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,220
to look for him?

370
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,480
Did you come to kill him?

371
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,000
Xuezhi,

372
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,840
I beg you.

373
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:27,680
Please don’t kill Qingmei.

374
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:29,040
-Fengzi.
-I beg you. Don’t kill Qingmei!

375
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:30,000
Get up. I won’t kill him.

376
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,160
I beg you.

377
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,040
Promise me, or I won’t get up.

378
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:34,400
I promise you. I won’t kill him.

379
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,160
Come on.

380
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,520
Get up. Come on.

381
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:38,600
I promise. Get up.

382
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:42,720
I promise.

383
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,160
But Fengzi,

384
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,440
do you know

385
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,460
why Xia Qingmei killed those men?

386
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,080
I don’t.

387
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,560
All I know is Qingmei

388
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,820
is working for Lord Lu.

389
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,400
As for what he’s done for him,

390
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,520
I have no idea.

391
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:08,589
So it is Xue Lie.

392
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:14,589
Xue Lie,

393
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,200
what do you want?

394
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,560
Rude man!

395
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,800
How dare

396
00:17:20,069 --> 00:17:22,440
you common men address Lord Lu by his name?

397
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,200
They’re my guests.

398
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,069
Xue Lie,

399
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:29,690
I know you slaughtered the small sects

400
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:31,480
because we opposed to the Sects Alliance

401
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,480
you proposed in Sword Manor.

402
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,720
Now

403
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,120
you drag us here.

404
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:38,880
What do you want?

405
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,240
Either

406
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,000
you let us go,

407
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,240
or

408
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,560
you kill us.

409
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:46,440
Make a choice!

410
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:49,160
It’s possible for me

411
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,600
to set you free.

412
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,480
I doubt it.

413
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:55,840
Tell me.

414
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:57,240
What is the price?

415
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:00,920
I admire martial artists

416
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,320
and would like to take any chances

417
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:05,320
to behold all kinds of martial arts.

418
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,160
As you can see,

419
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:09,680
this is my private hunting field.

420
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,690
There is a way out at the bottom of the hill.

421
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,480
We’ll remove

422
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:16,480
your shackles.

423
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,980
If you can defeat my Warriors in Black

424
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,000
and make it to the exit

425
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,140
before the incense burns out,

426
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,240
I’ll let you go.

427
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,480
It’s quite a surprise

428
00:18:42,480 --> 00:18:44,540
that the martial arts of the two sects

429
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,440
are so incredible.

430
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,140
I thought less of them before.

431
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,500
Your Highness,

432
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:54,970
I think it’s enough.

433
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,120
You can stop.

434
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,160
Yes.

435
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:01,440
Do you know when a man is desperate?

436
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,000
It’s when they believe…

437
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:03,320
Come on.

438
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:04,960
…there’s hope.

439
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,040
Go.

440
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,200
Fire.

441
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:24,170
Your Highness, they’re now in pieces.

442
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,080
What?

443
00:19:26,760 --> 00:19:28,320
They’re now in pieces.

444
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,600
Say it again.

445
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,560
They’re now in pieces.

446
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,120
Did you hear it?

447
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,520
In pieces.

448
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:41,280
No matter how good you are,

449
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:44,880
even if you’re made of iron,

450
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:48,320
I can blow you into pieces.

451
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:52,520
Hey,

452
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:53,320
is Fengzi

453
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:54,640
alright?

454
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:55,880
I don’t know.

455
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,490
What did you talk about?

456
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:58,840
The man we’re looking for

457
00:19:58,840 --> 00:19:59,840
is Xia Qingmei.

458
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:00,880
I was right.

459
00:20:01,280 --> 00:20:03,320
He killed the leader of Shark Sect, Tie Xiao,

460
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:04,560
turned to Lord Lu

461
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:06,360
and silenced different voices for him.

462
00:20:06,360 --> 00:20:07,280
So many lives

463
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:08,680
taken by him.

464
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,640
Many martial artists

465
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,040
are scared of Nine Moves

466
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:13,120
because of him.

467
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:14,960
He practiced Nine Moves

468
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,680
and killed innocent people

469
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,640
under cover.

470
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:20,560
While the world thinks you killed them.

471
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:23,080
You bear too much for him.

472
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:24,600
There’s no need to be tolerant.

473
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:26,000
It’s easier said than done.

474
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,480
He’s under Lord Lu’s protection

475
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:30,280
and he’s achieved the ninth move of the Nine Moves.

476
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:32,720
Though I’ve practiced Lotus Sutra,

477
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,580
he’s still more powerful than me.

478
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,720
Besides,

479
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:38,440
we don’t even know where he is

480
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,440
or where he’ll go.

481
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,760
Shangqing Sect is in danger?

482
00:20:44,040 --> 00:20:46,040
I don’t know who sent it,

483
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:47,840
or if it’s a trap.

484
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,120
But,

485
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,320
maybe we can find some clues

486
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:51,400
from this note.

487
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:52,880
What if it’s true?

488
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:54,200
Look,

489
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,440
let’s go back and meet with Zhusha and Chequ.

490
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:58,370
Then we’ll head to Shangqing Sect.

491
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,400
Sure.

492
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,540
Your Highness,

493
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,240
the Warriors in Black spying on Chong Xuezhi

494
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,120
are back.

495
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:08,320
Any news?

496
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:11,600
Chong Xuezhi has been missing

497
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,660
since Lin Changran took her away.

498
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,920
But two days ago,

499
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,320
she was spotted

500
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:18,580
in Xia Qingmei’s home.

501
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,080
And

502
00:21:20,760 --> 00:21:22,160
according to the scouts,

503
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,600
there was a young man with her

504
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,060
who looks a lot like

505
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,360
Shangguan Tou.

506
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:32,320
What?

507
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,340
Calm down, Your Highness.

508
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,320
They said like,

509
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:37,760
it may not be

510
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:38,620
Shangguan Tou.

511
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,120
Are you comforting me?

512
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,240
How many men

513
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:48,080
in this world do you think look like him?

514
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,480
It’s my fault.

515
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,960
I ask for your punishment.

516
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:54,880
Have they met Xia Qingmei?

517
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:00,240
Chong Xuezhi met

518
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,120
Lin Fengzi.

519
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,900
Women are all loose-tongued.

520
00:22:06,320 --> 00:22:09,120
Chong Xuezhi must have learned from Lin Fengzi

521
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:12,100
that Xia Qingmei loses his mind
from time to time

522
00:22:12,280 --> 00:22:14,340
because he’s practicing Nine Moves.

523
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:17,120
Xia Qingmei went to Yunlai Mountain.

524
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:18,120
Any news from him?

525
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:20,860
There will be soon.

526
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:24,600
Send Warriors in Black to Yunlai Mountain.

527
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:27,600
If they run into Chong Xuezhi and that man,

528
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:31,440
kill both of them.

529
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,620
Your Highness,

530
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,880
Xia Qingmei’s trip to Yunlai Mountain

531
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:39,960
is top secret.

532
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,060
Even Lin Fengzi doesn’t know.

533
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:43,240
How could

534
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:44,720
Chong Xuezhi know?

535
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,040
Sir,

536
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:48,840
just do as you’re told.

537
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:50,200
Yes.

538
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:51,240
Wait.

539
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,400
It’s about time

540
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:56,330
to honor my promise to Yuwen Muyuan

541
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:58,730
to let him take over Hall of Flames.

542
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,040
I want to see

543
00:23:01,040 --> 00:23:02,900
if sects in the martial arts world

544
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:04,400
have learned the lesson or not

545
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,600
after the cleansing.

546
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:07,980
Send out invitations.

547
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,520
Tell them I require their presence

548
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:12,340
at Yuwen Muyuan’s induction.

549
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,200
Yes.

550
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:16,040
To what honor do I owe

551
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,740
the guardians’ visit?

552
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:20,760
Leader Lin, do you know about

553
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:23,640
the massacres in the martial arts world?

554
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,320
The Sand Sect and the Purple Hawk Sect

555
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:28,120
are both brutally slaughtered.

556
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:30,160
I heard rumors about it.

557
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:32,280
I guess it’s just the conflict

558
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,480
between minor sects.

559
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:37,560
You might have a point.

560
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:39,780
But it’s quite strange

561
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,170
that these sects

562
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,160
were all killed with Nine Moves.

563
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:48,920
Are you sure?

564
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:52,120
The Hall of Flames has nothing to do with it.

565
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:55,000
It originates from the Hall of Flames,

566
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,000
but even our leader cannot

567
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,200
reach the top level in such a short time.

568
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:00,680
However, the murderer has mastered

569
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,260
the ninth level of the Nine Moves.

570
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:05,560
Leader Lin,

571
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,200
this man not only mastered the supreme martial art,

572
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:10,360
but he uses it to scourge
the martial arts world.

573
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:11,360
The Hall of Flames

574
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,480
is his scapegoat.

575
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,520
I know what you’re trying to say.

576
00:24:17,280 --> 00:24:19,480
This will come to light sooner or later.

577
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,240
The man you’re talking about

578
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:24,680
is likely Xia Qingmei.

579
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:27,940
Leader Lin, are you admitting

580
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,560
that Xia Qingmei practiced Nine Moves?

581
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,520
He was my disciple for ten years.

582
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:37,040
Yet I failed to see him through.

583
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,320
However, Lord Lu

584
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:41,600
sensed his ambition so clearly

585
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,760
and recruited him.

586
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:47,640
I failed in instructing him.

587
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,880
I was a poor master

588
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:52,680
and a sinner to the martial arts world.

589
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:53,600
Leader Lin,

590
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,800
This is not the time for remorse.

591
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,880
Xia Qingmei has achieved

592
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,680
the ninth level of the Nine Moves

593
00:25:00,080 --> 00:25:02,200
and has become Xue Lie’s puppet.

594
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:04,200
Xue Lie has ordered him to kill

595
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,860
any disobedient minor sects.

596
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,120
Once he does that,

597
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,930
he slaughters the entire sect.

598
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,320
Leaving him unrestrained,

599
00:25:10,320 --> 00:25:12,000
the decent and loyal men of martial arts world

600
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,800
will be all killed by him one day.

601
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:16,640
Though the fact that he has Lord Lu’s shelter,

602
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,560
Xia Qingmei

603
00:25:17,560 --> 00:25:19,020
has been extremely cruel.

604
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:22,660
We think because he’s been using Nine Moves,

605
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:25,420
he is now at the stage of obsessive insanity.

606
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,080
Insanity?

607
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:29,760
I’m afraid that

608
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:31,920
even as we speak, he’s killing people.

609
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:34,120
Leader Lin, are you going to do nothing?

610
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,240
I give you my word.

611
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,240
Xia Qingmei was my disciple.

612
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,280
I’m responsible.

613
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,060
I’ll do everything in my power

614
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,640
to stop him.

615
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,250
Chief Guardian,

616
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:52,680
how much can the Black Fire

617
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:54,040
empower a man like me

618
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,320
who doesn’t

619
00:25:57,040 --> 00:25:58,300
know any martial arts?

620
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,720
If I’m right,

621
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:07,360
the supreme martial arts in the world
is Nine Moves.

622
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:08,440
Do you think

623
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:11,000
it can defeat the Black Fire?

624
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,800
No.

625
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:16,960
If it cannot,

626
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,800
why do the martial artists

627
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:22,160
practice painstakingly each day?

628
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,000
We don’t practice

629
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:26,370
to pursue perfection in martial arts,

630
00:26:27,080 --> 00:26:28,280
but to guide our will.

631
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,200
You think too highly

632
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,520
of those ruffians.

633
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:32,960
They’re nothing

634
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:34,440
but dumb animals.

635
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:36,100
They know nothing about will.

636
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:43,730
Chief Guardian,

637
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:45,440
don’t mind it.

638
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:47,800
I’m not referring to you.

639
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:51,400
I guess you know

640
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:55,000
how much I admire you.

641
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:01,240
Yes, I do.

642
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:03,840
You’ve been working for me for some time.

643
00:27:03,840 --> 00:27:05,170
It’s time for me to honor

644
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,360
my promise to you.

645
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:09,960
You will assume the leadership of the Hall of Flames.

646
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,760
I have decided

647
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:12,820
to hold an induction ceremony for you

648
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,640
and invite guests from all sects

649
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,920
to be your witnesses.

650
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:17,440
From now on,

651
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,810
whether Chong Xuezhi is alive or dead,

652
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,360
the leader of Hall of Flames

653
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:23,200
can only be you, Yuwen Muyuan.

654
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,200
From now on,

655
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,280
the Hall of Flames is no longer

656
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:28,540
an evil sect shut down by the government,

657
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:31,000
but a decent sect with loyalty.

658
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:37,340
Thank you, Your Highness.

659
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:39,200
I’m thinking

660
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,930
to hold the induction ceremony

661
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,520
here at my mansion

662
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,880
to show you my sincerity.

663
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:45,820
What do you say?

664
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,040
It’s not simply

665
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,800
for my takeover

666
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:59,050
that you want it to be held here, right?

667
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,120
Uncle Lin.

668
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:10,920
Xuezhi.

669
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,600
Leader Lin.

670
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,120
Shangguan Tou?

671
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,360
As you can see, Leader Lin,

672
00:28:16,360 --> 00:28:17,420
I’m safe and sound.

673
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:21,700
When I heard of your death,

674
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,250
I felt extremely guilty

675
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:25,440
Leader Lin,

676
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,640
you need not to worry.

677
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,560
In fact,

678
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:29,960
I appreciate your help that day.

679
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:32,040
It was my plan

680
00:28:32,040 --> 00:28:33,040
to feign my death.

681
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,800
I fly low

682
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:37,240
to let Xue Lie’s guard down

683
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,600
and escape from his hunt.

684
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:40,960
By doing this, I can stop his next move.

685
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,360
Today,

686
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,600
we invite you here

687
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:46,280
to discuss one thing.

688
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:48,930
I’ve learned about what Qingmei has done.

689
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:50,850
Whatever he’s going to do next,

690
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:52,500
I’ll do my best to stop him.

691
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:54,920
I won’t draw back even if it means

692
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:56,140
the loss of my life.

693
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:59,000
We’re so grateful to you, Uncle Lin.

694
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,040
I heard news

695
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:02,560
that Xia Qingmei is likely

696
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:04,000
to go to Shangqing Sect.

697
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,120
It’s said

698
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:07,440
that Priest Xingyi and his disciples

699
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,600
are in secluded training at Yunlai Mountain.

700
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:10,760
Xia Qingmei is likely

701
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:12,960
to attack Yunlai Mountain.

702
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,480
If he succeeds,

703
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,740
Shangqing Sect

704
00:29:16,120 --> 00:29:18,120
will probably be slaughtered, too.

705
00:29:18,840 --> 00:29:20,170
What are we waiting for?

706
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:21,380
Let’s head out now.

707
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:22,640
Right.

708
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:24,840
It’s a great joy to talk to a smart man

709
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:25,560
like you.

710
00:29:26,560 --> 00:29:29,080
It’s been days since my proposal
of Sects Alliance.

711
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:30,000
The rogues

712
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,920
have been eliminated one by one.

713
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:33,800
I think

714
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:36,040
it’s time to set the alliance up.

715
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,380
So Your Highness intends to take this chance

716
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:41,490
to announce its establishment

717
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,800
during my induction

718
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:45,520
when sects leaders will all be present.

719
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:46,400
Right.

720
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:48,660
Your Highness,

721
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:50,560
well,

722
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,800
I hate to steal your show.

723
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,890
Since Your Highness wants to announce it,

724
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:58,120
I’d like to assume the leader of Hall of Flames

725
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,280
in another day.

726
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:00,320
Otherwise,

727
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:02,570
I’m afraid I’d overshadow you.

728
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,250
Chief Guardian,

729
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,520
I just complimented you on your loyalty.

730
00:30:10,320 --> 00:30:11,000
What?

731
00:30:12,120 --> 00:30:13,450
Have you lost your wits?

732
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:17,760
Your Highness,

733
00:30:18,600 --> 00:30:19,960
do you want me

734
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,500
to follow Lin Zongxing’s example

735
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,280
and be a puppet?

736
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,010
How dare you?

737
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,400
I’m an imperial lord.

738
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:30,170
It’s not proper for me
to summon martial artists.

739
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:32,520
When you came to me,

740
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:34,000
you shared my vision

741
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:35,560
to bring benefits to the martial arts world.

742
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:37,620
Now you’re going against your words.

743
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,720
Is that how you repay

744
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,320
my appreciation?

745
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,410
Forgive me, Your Highness.

746
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:45,800
I

747
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,250
will follow your order.

748
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,090
Chief Guardian,

749
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:00,960
I don’t want to hide behind you.

750
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:03,120
But in the martial arts world,

751
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:05,120
few men share the vision

752
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:06,560
we have.

753
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,440
If I come forward,

754
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,920
given my status,

755
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,760
there’ll be rumblings.

756
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,080
I just want to take

757
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:16,880
your induction as a chance

758
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,200
to do some pragmatic things.

759
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:22,000
I see.

760
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:23,520
Good.

761
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:25,240
If so,

762
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:28,180
I’d like you to run an errand to Huashan Sect.

763
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:30,680
Huashan Sect?

764
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,440
First, Feng Mo is dead.

765
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,800
Huashan Sect lost their leader.

766
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:37,400
I need an august man to discipline them.

767
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,440
Second,

768
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,730
Xiangzhou is small,

769
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:41,240
but it’s home to numerous talents.

770
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:44,040
Hall of Flames’ disciples
detained at Sword Manor

771
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:48,360
are waiting for you to take them home.

772
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:52,450
Yes, Your Highness.

773
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,320
Master Xia.

774
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:06,080
I knew Lord Lu would send men here,

775
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,650
but I never thought it’d be you.

776
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:09,800
Now that you do,

777
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:11,130
let’s cut the nonsense.

778
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:13,120
Answer me.

779
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,360
Are you in the Sects Alliance or not?

780
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:20,160
Supreme Lord, bless him.

781
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,280
Old Taoist!

782
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:24,080
You are

783
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:27,280
digging your own grave.

784
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:34,320
It seems you’re determined.

785
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:35,960
All right.

786
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,160
I’m in a mood to fight.

787
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:42,760
Let me send you to your maker!

788
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,240
Qingmei!

789
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:50,600
Master.

790
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:52,410
What are you doing here?

791
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:55,880
I know what you did.

792
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,640
I order you

793
00:32:58,280 --> 00:33:00,010
to go back with me immediately.

794
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:00,920
Master.

795
00:33:02,520 --> 00:33:03,780
It’s out of your hands.

796
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:06,280
Do you have any idea of what you’ve done?

797
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:09,160
When you left Sword Manor,

798
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:11,460
I thought it was just temper tantrum.

799
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:14,170
I never imagined you would do things so wrong!

800
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:15,560
Qingmei,

801
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,770
you’re still young.

802
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:19,780
Don’t make more mistakes.

803
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:22,600
Master.

804
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,010
Don’t come over!

805
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:28,180
If you still regard me as your master,

806
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:29,960
go back with me.

807
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,240
Don’t help the devil.

808
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:35,890
Have you forgotten the sect rules you learned

809
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,820
in the last decade?

810
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:42,940
I don’t understand

811
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:46,250
what’s so wrong about working for Lord Lu?

812
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,930
Isn’t it good to have a united world

813
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,640
with all sects in perfect order

814
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,080
and no more conflicts?

815
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,440
Master,

816
00:33:55,800 --> 00:33:57,730
isn’t that your dream for decades?

817
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:58,560
No!

818
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:01,120
The martial arts world needs diversity,

819
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,240
not tyranny!

820
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:04,240
Not to mention unrestrained killing

821
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,400
in the name of Sects Alliance!

822
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,400
Qingmei,

823
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,000
have some sense.

824
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,600
Think about Fengzi.

825
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:18,800
Let’s go home.

826
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,280
No.

827
00:34:28,190 --> 00:34:28,880
No.

828
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,420
I’m not going back.

829
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,920
I have work to do.

830
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:33,190
When it’s done,

831
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:35,120
I can build my own sect.

832
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,000
By then,

833
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:38,040
you all will have to bow to me!

834
00:34:39,560 --> 00:34:41,670
You have no sense of righteousness.

835
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,800
Even if you become a sect leader,

836
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:45,880
what would you do to win their trust?

837
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:46,630
Lin Zongxing,

838
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:48,150
you have no right to judge me.

839
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:49,760
I’ve learned all Nine Moves.

840
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,239
I’m the best in the world.

841
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:53,880
No one is strong enough to control me.

842
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,199
Even though you’ve learned Nine Moves,

843
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:58,080
you have no right to kill at will!

844
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:00,440
What you did

845
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,960
is against the rules of the martial arts world!

846
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:06,160
If you don’t stop now,

847
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:08,560
the whole world will jump at you!

848
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:13,760
In this world, the strongest is the king.

849
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,560
And the king

850
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:17,760
makes the rules.

851
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,320
I’m the best in the world.

852
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,450
Anyone who dares to get in my way

853
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:26,200
will have to die!

854
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,520
You’re not the best yet.

855
00:35:29,040 --> 00:35:30,040
Chong Xuezhi?

856
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,280
You’re not

857
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,120
until you defeat me.

858
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:39,000
You’re not dead?

859
00:35:40,520 --> 00:35:42,080
You lost to me years ago

860
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:44,040
in the Hero Assembly.

861
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,800
What gives you the courage

862
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:48,840
to challenge me?

863
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:50,760
I did lose to you

864
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:52,400
in the Hero Assembly.

865
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,620
But I’m no longer that person.

866
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,560
You stole my manual

867
